{"id":9600,"date":"2012-10-31T23:00:29","date_gmt":"2012-11-01T03:00:29","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=9600"},"modified":"2019-05-17T14:40:46","modified_gmt":"2019-05-17T10:40:46","slug":"tawhid-hunafa-fitrah-shaytan","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/31\/tawhid-hunafa-fitrah-shaytan\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Fitrah: Humans born to worship, but Satan leads astray"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>&#8216;Iyad ibn Himar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Verily, my Lord has commanded me to teach you what you do not know, from what he has taught me this day, &#8216;All wealth I bestowed upon them is lawful. I have created all of My servants inclined to worship, but devils come to them who turn them away from their religion. They outlaw what has been made lawful for them, and they command them to associate partners with Me for which no authority has been revealed.&#8217; Verily, Allah looked at the people of the earth and He detested all of them, Arabs and foreigners alike, except for remnants of the people of the Book<\/strong>.&#8221;<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2865<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0636\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062d\u0650\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e<strong> \u0623\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0627 \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0628\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0623\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0646\u0650\u064a \u0